OL,3,CManchester United confirm Ruben Amorim
OL,4,Cas new manager
OL,6,FSporting Lisbon manager Ruben Amorim
OL,7,Fhas been officially announced as
OL,8,FManchester United's new head coach.
OL,10,FThe Red Devils called time on Erik ten
OL,11,FHag's 29-month reign after the Old
OL,12,FTrafford it was unanimously decided
OL,13,Fenough was enough following the club's
OL,14,Floss at West Ham.
OL,16,FRuud van Nistelrooy was put in
OL,17,Ftemporary charge as United looked for
OL,18,Fa new boss, with the club informing
OL,19,FSporting Lisbon they would pay the
OL,20,F10million euros (#8.3m) termination
OL,21,Fclause in Amorim's contract.
