OL,3,CManchester United confirm Ruben Amorim
OL,4,Cas new manager
OL,6,FThe 39-year-old now becomes the sixth
OL,7,Fpermanent manager to try and bring
OL,8,Fback the glory days to Old Trafford
OL,9,Fsince United's legendary manager Sir
OL,10,FAlex Ferguson retired in 2013.
OL,12,FIn a statement, the club said:
OL,13,F"Manchester United is delighted to
OL,14,Fannounce the appointment of Ruben
OL,15,FAmorim as Head Coach of the men's
OL,16,Ffirst team. He will join Manchester
OL,17,FUnited on Monday 11 November once he
OL,18,Fhas fulfilled his obligations with
OL,19,FSporting CP.
