OL,4,Cas new manager
OL,6,F"Ruben is one of the most exciting and
OL,7,Fhighly rated young coaches in European
OL,8,Ffootball."
OL,10,FThe former Portugal international will
OL,11,Fsign a contract with Manchester United
OL,12,Funtil 2027 and will begin his new role
OL,13,Fduring the international break.
OL,15,FFans will have to wait nearly a month
OL,16,Ffor Amorim's first game in charge
OL,17,Fafter United and Sporting Lisbon
OL,18,Freportedly negotiated 30-day notice
OL,19,Fperiod for the coach.
