OL,6,FIt is hoped Amorim, whose side
OL,7,Fcurrently sits top of the Portuguese
OL,8,Ftable, will be present for United's
OL,9,Fgame against Chelsea at Old Trafford
OL,10,Fon Sunday.
OL,12,FAmorim has won two Portuguese titles
OL,13,Fand two League Cups with Sporting
OL,14,Fsince joining the club in March 2020.
OL,16,FSpeaking at a press conference on
OL,17,FThursday 31 October, Amorim promised
OL,18,Fto speak more on the appointment after
OL,19,Fhis current teams match against
OL,20,FEstrela Amadora on Friday 1 November.
