OL,6,FThe former Aston Villa forward said:
OL,7,F"I did do my coaching badges with him.
OL,8,FHe was one of the ones that was there
OL,9,Fand you could tell he was so into it
OL,10,Fin a way that he had to get his badges
OL,11,Fto go and start managing. He was very
OL,12,Ffocused.
OL,14,F"Since the start of last season,
OL,15,FSporting Lisbon have scored the most
OL,16,Fgoals in the top six leagues, 129
OL,17,Fgoals.
OL,19,F"They were waiting 19 years to win a
OL,20,Ftitle, he goes there and they've won
OL,21,Ftwo in the last five seasons.
